    public interface MatProcessorModule
extends Module

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static MatProcessorModule INERT_MAT_PROCESSOR
      This MatProcessorModule, named "inert_mat_processor", should be used whenever you want a mat processor that doesn't do anything - it just returns the input.
